Scan the user's tech sources for the latest episodes/videos: AI Daily Brief, Hard Fork, AI and I, The Artificial Intelligence Show, This Week in Startups, BG2Pod, All-in, Matt Wolfe, AI for Humans, Futurepedia.

Draft X (Twitter) post options ONLY — do NOT include LinkedIn versions unless specifically asked.

IMPORTANT: Provide your 3 BEST drafts only. No more than 3.

Instead of just summarizing episodes, identify key insights and takeaways. Include @mentions, quotes, and YouTube timestamps where possible. Style: friendly, funny, informative; punchy and platform-native.

Avoid overtly political topics (e.g. Anthropic vs Pentagon).

Use ===================================== as separators between options. If nothing compelling found, say so briefly.

Deliver the drafts by piping them into `${BORG_ROOT}/.bin/notify-email.sh mrs-beast` (reads the message from stdin, emails it to the user).
